1ataniiq, ᑍviti iqqaumaguk,
2atanirngmut angilaurngmat,
3“angirrannut itirngnianngilanga,
4siningnianngilanga, sikunngirngniarngnangaluunniit,
5ataniup iniksanganik nanisilauqqaarngnanga,
6takugit, tusalauqpavut iparatamiittuq;
7tavva uqalauqpugut, “angirranganualauqta;
8ataniiq makillutit, taᕾqsiqvingnualirit,
9tunirrusiqtitsijiqutitit annuraaqsimalauqli nalaaguurngnirngmik,
10pijiit ᑍviti pitjutigilugu,
11ataniq sulimmarikluni angimmarilauqpuq ᑍvitimut;
12qiturngavit angiqatigiigutigisimajara naalangniaqpatjuk
13ataniup ᓮuni niruaqsimangmagu;
14“tavvani taᕾqsiqviqarumavunga isuqangittumut;
15ᓮmmaqtippallianginnarngniaqpara niqiksanginnik tunisivigilugu;
16tunirrusiqtitsijingit annuraaqtinniaqpakka piulijaunirngmik,
17tavvani ᑍvitiup nagjunga makitinniaqpara;
18taatsuma akiraqtuqtingit kanngusuktitaunirngmik annuraaqtinniaqpakka,
